{"tid":1544920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"義士唔係Condom！#罷買捐助義士Challenge","createTime":"2019-09-05T17:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T18:21:34.000Z","uid":58883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c645d2b6526afc4fcabcbe5e186790614398043","tid":1544920,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:18:27.000Z","msg":"當初我地開始提倡日五罷買，除左想以經濟途徑去推動整個運動，仲想鼓勵大家儲錢捐比有需要既義士。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>星星之火 </strong></span><br />\n我同一眾義工呢個月省埋省埋都儲左唔少錢，呢兩日就一齊捐左星火同盟。<br />\n<strong>係呢度我地發起一個Challenge，如果你地成功罷買儲到錢去捐助義士，請Upload收據同 tag #罷買捐助義士Challenge，再share比身邊親友。</strong><br />\n<br />\n對比起612，星火同盟冇具名氣既發起人，但自從2014年，星火同盟一直好積極主動去幫受政治迫害既香港抗爭者，所有款項將全數用於義士及其家屬身上，星火同盟不會扣取一分一毫。<br />\n<em>以下係星火同盟既網站同捐款方法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2F&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=7cc210e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/</a><br />\n滙豐銀行: 048-857585-838<br />\n戶口全名: The Prime Management Service Ltd.<br />\n自動櫃員機戶口名字顯示: T PR**E M*L T*A T*C<br />\nFPS轉數快ID: 3771623<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bkXttt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bkXttt.jpg&h=42d45d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(當然大家可以捐比其他基金)</em><br />\n<br />\n我地相信香港人只有齊心協力，先至可以對抗社會既不公義；我地亦相信每一個人既力量都好重要，星星之火，可以燎原。六月至今被捕人數逾 1100 人，當中至少 70 人被控告暴動罪，示威者受傷人數更是難以統計。有好多年輕人為我地，為香港付出左好多，我地又可以付出幾多？其實金錢固然重要，但比義士合道大家肯幫佢地更加重要，所以千其唔好因為可以捐出既銀碼少而唔去做。<br />\n<br />\n依家香港係一個消費主義橫行既一個社會，廣告氾濫，商店林立，商家好似千方百計摧殘去我地既自信，簡接令我地不安和不快樂。試諗一上，花錢買左一件商品之後，通常大家既快樂又可以維持幾耐。然而，如果買唔到一件你係廣告上睇啱既商品，你既果種欲罷不能既感覺又會維持幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n其實大家將呢Ｄ不必要既消費，換做去幫有需要既人，所得到既心靈上既滿足可能比物質更持久更真實。我地亦都唔係呼籲大家苦行，其實就算唔捐都好，與其花費係不必要既物質，不如儲錢去學習新技能／進修／旅行探索充實人生。所以，小編希望大家繼續實行日五罷買，將省落黎既錢用得其所。<br />\n＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿<br />\n記我FOLLOW我地FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbyebuydayhk&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=3a4f981a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk</a><br />\n簽署承諾罷買︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ORv5Zw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ORv5Zw&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=faf4f1c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ORv5Zw</a><br />\nInstagram: @byebuydayhk<br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/sunfribyebuy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsunfribyebuy&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=6d29b608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sunfribyebuy</a><br />\nChannel: <a href=\"https://t.me/byebuydaychannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbyebuydaychannel&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=534cdab8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/byebuydaychannel</a><br />\n#日五罷買 #SunFriByeBuy<br />\n#罷買救港 #ByeBuySaveHK<br />\n#全民罷買日 #ByeBuyDayHK"},{"pid":"853d55533d30dd743783911bac982d0896742422","tid":1544920,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:18:34.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"beee36f74b7816d89a69b0df107a8b0ac5176d4b","tid":1544920,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vYzUvHz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvYzUvHz.jpg&h=ad15b0d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92ea85c3e1c6a94608038dc5ab4f990f51a1f117","tid":1544920,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:18:51.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》青馬大合唱！Singing On the Bridge!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544899</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2035d2b35e7357153b155bafe3965bf22d9c303f","tid":1544920,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:19:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8cb7b638eb2b3f6b2e4f9c44a30869b32204c87","tid":1544920,"uid":43311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:21:05.000Z","msg":"831 CCTV<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n907 機場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n908 美領 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fc5da40bbc00b26146fb4fc3ad4377451c96a6","tid":1544920,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:21:32.000Z","msg":"＃日五罷買"},{"pid":"4e2fcfd568bc28b80d476eef7fcb11a6baa7011b","tid":1544920,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67929653_112049723486814_8982519114232758272_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_eui2=AeF9ef_fLEG1kqigM19N2NUhdWoKjyWhROkWZ3xTMIrTc2LtErAhF85RKwRAmFLv91WMfTONGK53l8BmRV2rCoCTRY3afnsWjdRfYDMvVvyGpw&amp;_nc_oc=AQmd_JBJPXbslAzA0sy4bIj7eZLYsoHg4Z7oLUsthvLb9OZVUaekyhXBhiH_pvvfTko&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=0e494f292a58cac999111b560513cd7c&amp;oe=5DFFAD60\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67929653_112049723486814_8982519114232758272_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_eui2%3DAeF9ef_fLEG1kqigM19N2NUhdWoKjyWhROkWZ3xTMIrTc2LtErAhF85RKwRAmFLv91WMfTONGK53l8BmRV2rCoCTRY3afnsWjdRfYDMvVvyGpw%26_nc_oc%3DAQmd_JBJPXbslAzA0sy4bIj7eZLYsoHg4Z7oLUsthvLb9OZVUaekyhXBhiH_pvvfTko%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D0e494f292a58cac999111b560513cd7c%26oe%3D5DFFAD60&h=ad60bada&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4a238877a30b86e808c3a4403bff23d1c1f609d","tid":1544920,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c645d2b6526afc4fcabcbe5e186790614398043","tid":1544920,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:18:27.000Z","msg":"當初我地開始提倡日五罷買，除左想以經濟途徑去推動整個運動，仲想鼓勵大家儲錢捐比有需要既義士。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>星星之火 </strong></span><br />\n我同一眾義工呢個月省埋省埋都儲左唔少錢，呢兩日就一齊捐左星火同盟。<br />\n<strong>係呢度我地發起一個Challenge，如果你地成功罷買儲到錢去捐助義士，請Upload收據同 tag #罷買捐助義士Challenge，再share比身邊親友。</strong><br />\n<br />\n對比起612，星火同盟冇具名氣既發起人，但自從2014年，星火同盟一直好積極主動去幫受政治迫害既香港抗爭者，所有款項將全數用於義士及其家屬身上，星火同盟不會扣取一分一毫。<br />\n<em>以下係星火同盟既網站同捐款方法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2F&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=7cc210e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/</a><br />\n滙豐銀行: 048-857585-838<br />\n戶口全名: The Prime Management Service Ltd.<br />\n自動櫃員機戶口名字顯示: T PR**E M*L T*A T*C<br />\nFPS轉數快ID: 3771623<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bkXttt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bkXttt.jpg&h=42d45d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(當然大家可以捐比其他基金)</em><br />\n<br />\n我地相信香港人只有齊心協力，先至可以對抗社會既不公義；我地亦相信每一個人既力量都好重要，星星之火，可以燎原。六月至今被捕人數逾 1100 人，當中至少 70 人被控告暴動罪，示威者受傷人數更是難以統計。有好多年輕人為我地，為香港付出左好多，我地又可以付出幾多？其實金錢固然重要，但比義士合道大家肯幫佢地更加重要，所以千其唔好因為可以捐出既銀碼少而唔去做。<br />\n<br />\n依家香港係一個消費主義橫行既一個社會，廣告氾濫，商店林立，商家好似千方百計摧殘去我地既自信，簡接令我地不安和不快樂。試諗一上，花錢買左一件商品之後，通常大家既快樂又可以維持幾耐。然而，如果買唔到一件你係廣告上睇啱既商品，你既果種欲罷不能既感覺又會維持幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n其實大家將呢Ｄ不必要既消費，換做去幫有需要既人，所得到既心靈上既滿足可能比物質更持久更真實。我地亦都唔係呼籲大家苦行，其實就算唔捐都好，與其花費係不必要既物質，不如儲錢去學習新技能／進修／旅行探索充實人生。所以，小編希望大家繼續實行日五罷買，將省落黎既錢用得其所。<br />\n＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿<br />\n記我FOLLOW我地FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbyebuydayhk&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=3a4f981a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk</a><br />\n簽署承諾罷買︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ORv5Zw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ORv5Zw&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=faf4f1c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ORv5Zw</a><br />\nInstagram: @byebuydayhk<br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/sunfribyebuy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsunfribyebuy&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=6d29b608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sunfribyebuy</a><br />\nChannel: <a href=\"https://t.me/byebuydaychannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbyebuydaychannel&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=534cdab8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/byebuydaychannel</a><br />\n#日五罷買 #SunFriByeBuy<br />\n#罷買救港 #ByeBuySaveHK<br />\n#全民罷買日 #ByeBuyDayHK"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:29:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59c3d71949c028d10c446ee3651fd1cd60e006ef","tid":1544920,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:47:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"615ad2568eab4a855a68fa34ee706f804f1ee290","tid":1544920,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:49:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cfcc3a1b929905ad859bd6f6879fb50125dafb96","tid":1544920,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:52:08.000Z","msg":"發夢罷食App 已經上架<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425586</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"43a63f96ccbd1b04098d61e74629de4b5b7efb7b","tid":1544920,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:22:36.000Z","msg":"3333"},{"pid":"071b279cb434538df8f8218e6f519647d0d58f75","tid":1544920,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:21:34.000Z","msg":"SSSSSSSSSSSS"}]}